These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | cola  | mirinda   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | martial-arts   |
| Sport         | biathlon | water-polo |
| Transport     | ship | scooter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, carrot
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, drama
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike
1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peas     | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller  |
| Pet           | hamster         | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | ship   | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, librarian
2 different pets are kept: dog, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | 7up     | coffee |
| Job         | librarian | musician    |
| Pet         | dog         | ferret        |
| Transport   | trike         | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
