There 2 different types of food: grapes, plum
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, singing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person eating plum is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | juice |
| Food          | plum   | grapes  |
| Hobby         | writing | singing     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | electronic         |

