.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, entrepreneur
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, canadian
2 different pets are kept: pony, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the entrepreneur is the italian##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | dancer    |
| Nationality   | italian       | canadian |
| Pet           | pony         | snake    |
| Sport         | parkour    | snowboarding   |

